@node Main "Obliks - Documentation"

                              'Obliks' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Obliks' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to position
diagonal mirrors, so they reflect rays that start from two entries
(one located at the top and the other is located at the bottom of
the game board) to the exits (of which one is located at the left
and the other is located at the right). The more mirrors that are
used and if their numbers are equal for both ray path, the better
it is...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves...

  Have fun!

